<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Proposition de Partenariat - Gala des PME</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
            color: #334155;
            font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 100% !important;
        }

        table {
            border-spacing: 0;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
        }

        td {
            padding: 0;
        }

        img {
            border: 0;
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
            display: block;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #C41230;
        }

        h1,
        h2,
        h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            color: #0F172A;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed;
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #0F172A;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png');
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 40px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #0F172A;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #94A3B8;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #C41230;
            color: #FFFFFF !important;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .info-table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .info-table td {
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #F1F5F9;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #334155;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #64748B;
            width: 40%;
        }

        .info-value {
            color: #0F172A;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px !important;
            }

            .container {
                width: 100% !important;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <table role="presentation" class="container" align="center">
            <tr>
                <td class="header">
                    <img src="https://admin.galadespmeci.com/images/mail/logo.png" alt="Gala des PME" width="120" style="margin: 0 auto; display: block;" />
                    <div
                        style="margin-top: 15px; height: 1px; width: 40px; background-color: #C41230; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                    </div>
                    <p
                        style="color: #D4AF37; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                        L'Excellence Entrepreneuriale</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #C41230;">Proposition de Partenariat</h1>
                    <p style="text-align: center; color: #64748B; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px;">Collaboration
                    </p>

                    <p>Bonjour <strong>{{dossier.nomRep}}</strong>,</p>

                    <p>Merci pour votre proposition de partenariat au nom de <strong>{{dossier.nomEntreprise}}</strong>. Nous croyons
                        fermement que les grandes réussites naissent de collaborations solides.</p>

                    <div style="background-color: #F8FAFC; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
                        <h3
                            style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #E2E8F0; padding-bottom: 10px;">
                            Détails de la Proposition</h3>
                        <table class="info-table">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Organisation</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{dossier.nomEntreprise}}</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Type de Partenariat</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{dossier.type}}</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Pack</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{dossier.package}}</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-label">Contribution</td>
                                <td class="info-value">{{dossier.raison}}</td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <p><strong>Suite donnée :</strong></p>
                    <p>Nous allons étudier les synergies possibles entre nos entités. Un membre de notre comité
                        d'organisation reviendra vers vous pour explorer les pistes de collaboration.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    <p
                        style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 16px;">
                        Gala des PME 2026</p>
                    <p>Sofitel Abidjan Hôtel Ivoire • Boulevard Hassan II</p>
                    <p><a href="tel:+2252722482626" style="color: #94A3B8; text-decoration: none;">+225 27 22 48 26
                            26</a> • <a href="mailto:partenariats@galadespme.com"
                            style="color: #94A3B8; text-decoration: none;">partenariats@galadespme.com</a></p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>

</html>